lead_paragraph: The president called on Congress to work with him on overhauling health care, changing the tax code and rebuilding the nation’s infrastructure and military.

byline.original: By JULIE HIRSCHFELD DAVIS, MICHAEL D. SHEAR and PETER BAKER

headline.main: Trump, in Optimistic Address, Asks Congress to End ‘Trivial Fights’
headline.print_headline: Before Congress, Trump Urges End to ‘Trivial Fights’
